                <h1>Discover the Enigmatic Ruins of Pompeii</h1>
                <p>Pompeii, an ancient Roman city, was frozen in time by the catastrophic eruption of Mount Vesuvius in 79 AD. This disaster preserved buildings, artifacts, and even the remains of its residents. Today, Pompeii is a UNESCO World Heritage site, drawing millions of visitors to explore its rich history and learn about the lives of its people.</p>
